What is CloudWatch?
Monitoring and observability service.

What Can Be Monitored?

EC2:
CPU
Memory
Disk

RDS:
Connections
CPU
Storage

Lambda:
Invocations
Errors

CloudWatch Components:

Metrics
Performance data.

Logs
Application logs.

Alarms
Notifications when thresholds exceed.

Real-Time Scenario:
Production Server

CPU > 80%
     ↓
CloudWatch Alarm
     ↓
SNS
     ↓
Email Alert

DevOps Engineer immediately notified.

Interview Questions:
Difference Between CloudWatch and CloudTrail?

CloudWatch = Monitoring
CloudTrail = Auditing
